  <brief_title>Post-marketing Surveillance of Atrovent® Inhalets in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Post-marketing Surveillance (as Per § 67(6) AMG [German Drug Law]) of Atrovent® Inhalets in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
